 |date=12 September 2018 |language=pt-BR}}</ref> [[iFood]],<ref>{{Cite web |last=Ferreira |first=Matheus |date=2017-08-20 |title=Anitta é a estrela de novo comercial do iFood |url=https://gkpb.com.br/21724/anitta-ifood-comercial/ |access-date=2023-01-31 |website=GKPB - Geek Publicitário |language=pt-BR}}</ref> [[Pepsi]],<ref>{{Cite web |date=2016-03-08 |title=Pepsi Twist lança personagem feminino dublado por Anitta |url=https://propmark.com.br/pepsi-twist-lanca-personagem-feminino-dublado-por-anitta/ |access-date=2023-01-31 |website=propmark |language=pt}}</ref> [[Magazine Luiza]],<ref>{{Cite web |last=Santos |first=Alana |date=2021-07-10 |title=Hit do Magalu, com Lu e Anitta, bate 1 milhão de visualizações em uma hora no Twitter |url=https://www.publicitarioscriativos.com/hit-do-magalu-com-lu-e-anitta-bate-1-milhao-de-visualizacoes-em-uma-hora-no-twitter/ |access-date=2023-01-31 |website=Publicitários Criativos |language=pt-BR}}</ref> [[Target Corporation|Target]],<ref>{{Cite web |date=2020-11-06 |title=Música de Anitta para campanha publicitária nos Estados Unidos cai na web |url=https://portalpopmais.com.br/musica-de-anitta-para-campanha-publicitaria-nos-estados-unidos-cai-na-web/ |access-date=2023-01-31 |website=portalpopmais.com.br |language=pt-BR}}</ref> Cadiveu, [[The Sims]],<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-11-16 |title=Anitta no The Sims 4: cantora grava música em Simlish; ouça! |url=https://meups.com.br/noticias/anitta-no-the-sims-4-simlish-practice/ |access-date=2023-01-31 |language=pt-BR}}</ref> [[Free Fire (video game)|Free Fire]],<ref>{{Cite web |last=Lopes |first=Léo |title=Anitta chega ao Free Fire: "Intenção é promover mulheres nos jogos on-line" |url=https://www.cnnbrasil.com.br/entretenimento/anitta-chega-ao-free-fire-intencao-e-promover-mulheres-nos-jogos-on-line/ |access-date=2023-01-31 |website=CNN Brasil |date=29 June 2022 |language=pt-BR}}</ref> [[Facebook Gaming]],<ref>{{Cite web |last=Canaltech |date=2020-08-24 |title=Anitta fará streaming de jogos com exclusividade no Facebook Gaming |url=https://canaltech.com.br/redes-sociais/anitta-fara-streaming-de-jogos-com-exclusividade-no-facebook-gaming-170472/ |access-date=2023-01-31 |website=Canaltech |language=pt-BR}}</ref> Brizza Arezzo,<ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta e Bruna Marquezine estrelam juntas campanha da Brizza Arezzo |website=Metrópoles |author=Ilca Maria Estevao |date=25 November 2022 |url=https://www.metropoles.com/colunas/ilca-maria-estevao/anitta-e-bruna-marquezine-brizza-arezzo |access-date=25 July 2023 |language=pt-BR |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221125215007/https://www.metropoles.com/colunas/ilca-maria-estevao/anitta-e-bruna-marquezine-brizza-arezzo |archive-date=25 November 2022}}</ref> Sol de Janeiro,<ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta Is Your Favorite Singer's Favorite Singer — and She Just Launched Her First Fragrance |url=https://www.instyle.com/beauty/anitta-sol-de-janeiro-fragrance-interview |access-date=2023-01-31 |website=InStyle |language=en}}</ref> Hope,<ref>{{Cite news |title=Anitta é a estrela de lançamentos da HOPE neste final de ano |url=https://topview.com.br/fashion/anitta-estrela-lancamentos-de-final-de-ano-da-hope/ |access-date=May 4, 2025 |website=Topview |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212105435/https://topview.com.br/fashion/anitta-estrela-lancamentos-de-final-de-ano-da-hope/ |archive-date=December 12, 2020}}</ref> [[Tiffany & Co.|Tiffany & Co]], [[Mercado Pago]],<ref>{{Cite web |title=Mercado Pago relança marca e junta Anitta por liderança na América Latina |url=https://www.cnnbrasil.com.br/economia/negocios/mercado-pago-deve-ter-maior-parte-do-aporte-de-r-34-bi-do-mercado-livre/ |date=April 22, 2025 |website=CNN Brasil |language=pt-BR |access-date=May 4, 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250422201117/https://www.cnnbrasil.com.br/economia/negocios/mercado-pago-deve-ter-maior-parte-do-aporte-de-r-34-bi-do-mercado-livre/ |archive-date=April 22, 2025}}</ref> among other brands.

In 2014, Anitta founded the Rodamoinho group, a [[holding company]] for music and entertainment with offices in [[Rio de Janeiro]] and [[Los Angeles]]. The holding has the companies, "Rodamoinho Entretenimento" which is specifically aimed at the production and realization of concerts, events and tours. "Rodamoinho Records" is a company dedicated to the music industry as a whole, which in addition to being a label and publisher, also carries out a survey of catalogs, registration of works, release and distribution of [[Single (music)|singles]], [[EPs]] and [[album]]s, management and organization of the musical collection and commercial negotiation of use and synchronization. "Rodamoinho Filmes" is an audiovisual production company, responsible for the production, execution, and delivery of videoclips, lives, and films. Who is also responsible for the idealization and executive production of the cartoon based on the life of the singer, "Clube da Anittinha". And "Floresta Music & Touring" which is a company dedicated to the management and international publishing of Brazilian artists.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Grupo Rodamoinho |url=https://rodamoinho.art.br/?lang=en |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Grupo Rodamoinho |language=en-US}}</ref>

In September 2019, the singer became Head of Creativity and Innovation at [[Skol|Skol Beats]], a brand of [[Ambev]], one of the largest breweries in the world.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Alves |first=Mayk |date=2019-09-27 |title=Ambev é a maior cervejaria do mundo e domina o mercado brasileiro |url=https://agro20.com.br/ambev/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Agro20 |language=pt-BR}}</ref> Anitta has been active in the discussion of marketing strategy, business and innovations. The contract provides for the launch of an authorial product per year.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta vira chefe de inovação da Ambev |url=https://epocanegocios.globo.com/Empresa/noticia/2019/09/anitta-vira-chefe-de-inovacao-de-cervejaria.html |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Época Negócios |date=23 August 2022 |language=pt-br}}</ref> Anitta launched, together with the [[antiperspirant]] brand [[Rexona]], a new product line "Rexona by Anitta" in 2019.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2020-01-24 |title=Anitta assina linha de desodorantes para Rexona |url=https://propmark.com.br/anitta-assina-linha-de-desodorantes-para-rexona/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=propmark |language=pt}}</ref> In November 2022, the singer now became the face of all Rexona 72h campaigns.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Rezende |first=Polly |date=2022-11-07 |title=Anitta agora é rosto de todas as campanhas de Rexona 72h |url=https://gkpb.com.br/107334/anitta-rexona-72h/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=GKPB - Geek Publicitário |language=pt-BR}}</ref>

On 16 January 2021, the singer signed a partnership with the [[Vegan products|vegan product]] brand, Cadiveu Essentials, a repair line, which has five products for a [[hair care]] routine. Anitta, in addition to becoming the brand's poster girl, co-created the Vegan Repair products alongside the brand's product development team.<ref>{{Cite web |last=themusicjournalbrazil |title=Anitta firma parceria com marca de produtos veganos |url=https://www.terra.com.br/diversao/musica/anitta-firma-parceria-com-marca-de-produtos-veganos,a7a05cdbfb2de10cdc433754f020f4d7ft3zo44e.html |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Terra |language=pt-BR}}</ref>

On 21 June 2021, Anitta was announced as a member of the board of directors of [[neobank]] [[Nubank]], the largest [[fintech]] bank in [[Latin America]], in addition to participating in the quarterly meetings with the company's board of directors to assist in strategic decisions about the future and improvement of the services offered by fintech to the most vulnerable classes.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Nubank |first=Redação |date=2021-06-21 |title=Anitta é a nova membro do conselho do Nubank |url=https://blog.nubank.com.br/anitta-nubank-membro-conselho/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Fala, Nubank |language=pt-br}}</ref> According to information from executives in [[interview]]s, the singer played a key role in convincing the board of the importance of listing the company on the Brazilian [[stock exchange]], [[B3 (stock exchange)|B3]], along with the planned [[IPO]] in the [[United States]]. In addition to supporting the idea of the company offering free stock receipts, BDR, to its customer base. With this initiative, fintech gained more than 7.5 million partners.<ref>{{Cite web |title=O poder da cantora Anitta dentro do Nubank |url=https://veja.abril.com.br/economia/o-que-a-cantora-anitta-faz-no-nubank/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=VEJA |language=pt-BR}}</ref> In August 2022, due to the growth of the singer's [[schedule]], due to her global expansion, Anitta requested that her participation in the board not be renewed. She then became a global brand ambassador, as part of Nubank's marketing, the singer participated in Nubank's campaign as a [[Sponsor (commercial)|sponsor]] of the [[2022 FIFA World Cup|2022 World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta deixa conselho do Nubank e assume posto de embaixadora global da marca |url=https://www.cnnbrasil.com.br/business/anitta-deixa-conselho-do-nubank-e-assume-posto-de-embaixadora-global-da-marca/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=CNN Brasil |date=9 August 2022 |language=pt-BR}}</ref>

On 23 May 2022, together with the [[educational institution]] [[YDUQS|Estácio]], the singer launched the [[online course]] "Anitta Prepara", a course aimed at the area of [[entrepreneurship]]. Anitta provides mentoring and is supported by a team of [[professor]]s from the [[higher education institution]], all of whom specialize in [[entrepreneurship]] and [[innovation]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-05-25 |title=Anitta lança curso de empreendedorismo com Estácio |url=https://portalmakingof.com.br/anitta-lanca-curso-de-empreendedorismo-com-estacio/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Portal Making Of |language=pt-BR |archive-date=29 January 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230129231515/https://portalmakingof.com.br/anitta-lanca-curso-de-empreendedorismo-com-estacio/ |url-status=dead }}</ref> On 26 May, the singer was announced as a partner of the Brazilian [[Food technology|foodtech]] focused on [[plant-based meats]], Fazenda Futuro (or Future Farm, its brand in the U.S.). Anitta participates in the company's business management, in addition to working on innovation projects that will help the brand to spread the consumption of [[meat]] made from [[plant]]s in Brazil and in other [[countries]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-05-26 |title=Anitta se torna sócia da Fazenda Futuro e vai ajudar a popularizar carne de plantas |url=https://exame.com/negocios/anitta-se-torna-socia-da-fazenda-futuro-e-vai-ajudar-a-popularizar-carne-de-plantas/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Exame |language=pt-br}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=d'Ávila |first=Mariana |date=2022-05-26 |title=Brazilian Pop Star Anitta Takes Stake in Plant-Based Startup Future Farm |url=https://www.bloomberglinea.com/2022/05/26/brazils-pop-star-anitta-takes-stake-on-plant-based-startup-future-farm/ |access-date=2023-03-06 |website=Bloomberg Línea |language=en-US}}</ref>

As a co-creator and in partnership with the [[pharmaceutical company]] Cimed, Anitta launched on 28 July 2022, the brand "Puzzy By Anitta", which is an intimate [[perfume]] without gender, with several [[fragrances]] inspired by the singer.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Matos|first=Lorena |date=2022-07-28 |title=Puzzy by Anitta: Cantora lança fragrância para região íntima em parceria com Cimed |url=https://www.moneytimes.com.br/puzzy-by-anitta-cantora-lanca-fragrancia-para-regiao-intima-em-parceria-com-cimed/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=Money Times |language=pt-br}}</ref> The intimate perfume, [[dermatologically]] and gynecologically tested, approved by [[Anvisa]], registered more than 400,000 units sold and the forecast is to close the first semester with a turnover of 50 million [[reais]]. The company also made the product available for international sale in the [[United States]] and [[Latin America]], in addition to the promise to make it available in [[Europe]], making "Puzzy by Anitta" the first Cimed product to be sold outside Brazil.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2023-01-06 |title=Puzzy by Anitta anuncia três novas fragrâncias e ação para o Carnaval |url=https://propmark.com.br/puzzy-by-anitta-anuncia-tres-novas-fragrancias-e-acao-para-o-carnaval/ |access-date=2023-01-29 |website=propmark |language=pt}}</ref>

==Personal life==
Anitta is [[bisexual]] and identifies as part of the [[LGBT community|LGBTQ+ community]].<ref>{{cite web |last=Levine |first=Nick C |url=https://www.dazeddigital.com/music/article/45680/1/anitta-brazil-pop-star-2019-interview |title=How Anitta became Brazil's biggest pop star |website=[[Dazed]] |date=19 August 2019 |access-date=29 May 2020 |quote=I have a huge LGBT audience, and I'm bisexual – but when you see me, if I don't ''tell you'' I'm bisexual, I don't have the physical representation of the LGBT (community).}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://anamariabraga.globo.com/acorda-menina/gente/anitta-assume-bissexualidade |title=Anitta assume sua bissexualidade: "faço parte da comunidade LGBTQ+" |date=19 September 2018 |access-date=2 February 2019}}</ref> She dated [[Mr. Thug]], the lead vocalist of [[Bonde da Stronda]], from early 2011 until the end of 2012.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://extra.globo.com/famosos/mc-anitta-posa-com-namorado-revela-gente-bem-foguento-veja-as-fotos-3950919.html |work=Globo.com |publisher=Extra |first=Thiago |last=Trindade |title=MC Anitta posa com o namorado e revela: 'a gente é bem foguento'. |date=12 February 2012 |access-date=27 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://entretenimento.r7.com/musica/fotos/musa-do-funk-conheca-as-curvas-da-sensual-anitta-20121105-13.html |work=R7 |title=Musa do funk: Conheça as curvas da sensual Anitta |access-date=27 October 2014 |archive-date=1 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201035414/http://entretenimento.r7.com/musica/fotos/musa-do-funk-conheca-as-curvas-da-sensual-anitta-20121105-13.html |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://entretenimento.r7.com/jovem/fotos/veja-o-charme-de-diego-thug-do-bonde-da-stronda-20121216-9.html |title=Veja o charme de Diego Thug, do Bonde da Stronda |access-date=27 October 2014 |archive-date=1 December 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201044348/http://entretenimento.r7.com/jovem/fotos/veja-o-charme-de-diego-thug-do-bonde-da-stronda-20121216-9.html |url-status=dead }}</ref> The singer also had a relationship with her dancer Ohana Lefundes,<ref name="natelinha.uol.com.br">{{Cite web |title=Anitta é surpreendida com relato de ex-namorado em programa de TV: "Ela é meio podre" |url=https://natelinha.uol.com.br/famosos/2020/06/12/anitta-recebe-depoimentos-de-ex-namorados-em-programa-de-tv-meio-podre-146363.php |access-date=27 March 2022 |website=NaTelinha |language=pt-br}}</ref>  with the doctor Pamela Tosatti<ref name="natelinha.uol.com.br"/> and with the actor and model Pablo Morais.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ego.globo.com/famosos/noticia/2016/07/termina-relacionamento-de-anitta-e-pablo-morais.html |title=Termina relacionamento de Anitta e Pablo Morais |work=Ego.com |access-date=27 October 2014}}</ref> On 17 November 2017, she married businessman Thiago Magalhães, with whom she had been in contact since May of the same year. The couple married under separation of property.<ref>{{cite journal |access-date=27 October 2014 |title=Anitta se casa com empresário Thiago Magalhães |url=http://f5.folha.uol.com.br/celebridades/2017/11/anitta-e-thiago-magalhaes-estao-casados-diz-colunista.shtml |journal=F5}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |access-date=27 October 2014 |title=Anitta diz que está muito feliz com casamento com Thiago Magalhães |url=https://f5.folha.uol.com.br/celebridades/2017/11/anitta-diz-que-esta-muito-feliz-com-casamento-com-thiago-magalhaes.shtml |journal=F5}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Anitta se casou com Thiago Magalhães em separação total de bens. Entenda! |url=http://www.purepeople.com.br/noticia/anitta-e-thiago-magalhaes-se-casaram-com-separacao-total-de-bens_a203862/1 |website=Purepeople |language=pt-BR |access-date=27 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.correio24horas.com.br/single-entretenimento/noticia/veja-primeira-foto-de-anitta-com-novo-namorado/?cHash=0beb4587589a471248164572a7c8ec72 |title=Veja primeira foto de Anitta com novo namorado |work=Correio (jornal) |access-date=27 October 2014 |archive-date=10 July 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710040949/http://www.correio24horas.com.br/single-entretenimento/noticia/veja-primeira-foto-de-anitta-com-novo-namorado/?cHash=0beb4587589a471248164572a7c8ec72 |url-status=dead }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.correiobraziliense.com.br/app/noticia/diversao-e-arte/2017/11/17/interna_diversao_arte,641590/anitta-casou-com-o-empresario-thiago-magalhaes-afirma-colunista.shtml |title=Anitta casou com o empresário Thiago Magalhães, afirma colunista |work=[[Correio Braziliense]] |date=17 November 2011 |access-date=27 October 2014}}</ref> They announced their divorce in September 2018.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://navva.org/brazil/entertainment/anitta-is-far-from-social-networks-after-divorce-and-fans-have-noticed-it/ |title=Anitta is far from social networks after divorce and fans have noticed it! |access-date=26 November 2018 |archive-date=27 November 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181127022519/https://navva.org/brazil/entertainment/anitta-is-far-from-social-networks-after-divorce-and-fans-have-noticed-it/ |url-status=dead }}</ref> She has had brief relationships with Pedro Scooby,<ref>{{cite web |title=Anitta e Pedro Scooby assumem namoro |url=https://www.correiobraziliense.com.br/app/noticia/diversao-e-arte/2019/06/01/interna_diversao_arte,759383/anitta-e-pedro-scooby-estao-namorando.shtml |work=Correio Braziliense |date=1 June 2019 |access-date=3 June 2019 |language=pt-BR |first=Correio |last=Braziliense}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://metropoles.com/colunas-blogs/pipocando/pedro-scooby-fala-sobre-fim-com-anitta-ela-terminou-por-telefone/amp |title=Pedro Scooby fala sobre fim com Anitta:"Ela terminou por telefone" |date=30 August 2019 |access-date=5 September 2019 |work=[[Metrópoles]] |language=pt-BR}}</ref> Gabriel David,<ref>{{cite web |title=Anitta assume namoro com sambista Gabriel David - Emais |url=https://emais.estadao.com.br/noticias/gente,anitta-assume-namoro-com-sambista-gabriel-david,70003250432 |work=Estadão |access-date=12 July 2020 |language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Acabou! Anitta termina relacionamento com empresário Gabriel David |url=https://www.purepeople.com.br/noticia/fim-de-namoro-anitta-esta-solteira-apos-relacao-com-empresario-gabriel-david_a292225/1 |work=www.purepeople.com.br |date=30 March 2020 |access-date=12 July 2020 |language=br}}</ref> television host Gui Araújo,<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://capricho.abril.com.br/entretenimento/apos-video-juntos-gui-araujo-confirma-namoro-com-anitta-em-live/ |title=Após vídeo juntos, Gui Araújo confirma namoro com Anitta em live |website=Capricho |date=7 May 2020 |language=pt |trans-title=After video together, Gui Araújo confirms dating with Anitta in live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://revistaquem.globo.com/QUEM-News/noticia/2020/05/gui-araujo-fala-sobre-namoro-com-anitta-e-quarentena-em-casal-ela-e-um-icone-de-fogosidade.html |title=Gui Araújo fala sobre namoro com Anitta e quarentena em casal: "Ela é um ícone de fogosidade" |website=Quem |date=27 August 2022 |language=pt |trans-title=Gui Araújo talks about dating with Anitta and quarantine as a couple: "She's an icon of fire"}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Anitta confirma fim de namoro com Gui Araújo: "Estou solteira" |url=https://revistaquem.globo.com/QUEM-News/noticia/2020/07/anitta-confirma-fim-de-namoro-com-gui-araujo.html |work=Quem |access-date=20 July 2020 |language=pt-br}}</ref> and [[Canadian]] record producer [[Murda Beatz]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Anitta assume namoro com produtor Murda Beatz no Dia dos Namorados|url= https://capricho.abril.com.br/entretenimento/anitta-assume-namoro-com-produtor-murda-beatz-no-dia-dos-namorados/ |work=Capricho |date= 13 June 2022 |access-date=13 June 2022 |language=pt-br}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-06-16 |title=Singer Anitta Is Dating Producer Murda Beatz |url=https://www.eonline.com/news/1334778/singer-anitta-is-dating-producer-murda-beatz |access-date=2022-09-28 |website=E! Online}}</ref> [[Maluma]] stated in an interview that he and Anitta had a romance and loved each other very much, but because they were in the same career, the relationship didn't move forward. "[...] It doesn't work for me to be in relationships with people from the industry. When it happened, with Anitta actually, she was just starting her (international) career. I met her and we really liked each other and all that. I thought to myself: 'I can't be with her, because she does the same thing as me.' [...]".<ref>{{Cite web |date=2023-03-27 |title=Maluma confirma ter vivido romance com Anitta: "A gente se gostava muito" {{!}} Donna |url=https://gauchazh.clicrbs.com.br/donna/gente/noticia/2023/03/maluma-confirma-ter-vivido-romance-com-anitta-a-gente-se-gostava-muito-clfr4f1k8007k0151f6hmvda7.html |access-date=2023-05-12 |website=GZH |language=pt-BR}}</ref> In July 2023, the Italian actor Simone Susinna appeared alongside the singer in Europe, confirming their romantic relationship.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2023-07-11 |title=Anitta e Simone Susinna: seis momentos que provam que o ator italiano está caidinho pela cantora |url=https://gshow.globo.com/tudo-mais/tv-e-famosos/noticia/anita-e-simone-susinna-seis-momentos-que-provam-que-o-ator-italiano-esta-caidinho-pela-cantora.ghtml |access-date=2023-08-06 |website=gshow |language=pt-br}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta tem namoro exposto por Simone Sussinna: "Minha esposa" |url=https://www.terra.com.br/diversao/musica/anitta-tem-namoro-exposto-por-simone-sussinna-minha-esposa,9773e4cf9bf4fe6cceb64e5abd8aced35nr1gyyl.html |access-date=2023-08-06 |website=Terra |language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta se irrita e rebate comentários sobre namoro com ator: "Não admito" |url=https://www.metropoles.com/colunas/fabia-oliveira/anitta-se-irrita-e-rebate-comentarios-sobre-namoro-com-ator-nao-admito |access-date=2023-08-06 |website=Metrópoles |date=2 August 2023 |language=pt}}</ref>

In an interview for ''Trip'' magazine in 2017, she stated that if she did not pursue her artistic career, she would "be a happy [[psychologist]]".<ref name="trip2">{{cite web |author=Cortêz, Natacha |date=17 May 2017 |title=Onipresença de Anitta |url=https://revistatrip.uol.com.br/trip/paginas-negras-entrevista-com-a-cantora-anitta-uma-das-maiores-artistas-pop-do-brasil-e-que-esta-planejando-carreira-internacional |access-date=17 March 2018}}</ref>

In January 2019, after watching the documentary ''[[Cowspiracy]]'' (2014), she started transitioning to [[veganism]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://mercyforanimals.org.br/anitta-afirma-que-virou-vegana-h-10-dias |title=Anitta afirma que virou vegana há 10 dias |publisher=[[Mercy for Animals]] |first=Mayra |last=Corrêa |date=9 January 2019 |access-date=2 February 2019}}</ref> but in May 2019, she said was not vegan anymore.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.vista-se.com.br/anitta-revela-que-deixou-de-ser-vegana-mas-diz-que-ja-esta-fazendo-adaptacoes-para-voltar/ |title=Anitta revela que deixou de ser vegana, mas diz que ja esta fazendo adaptacoes para voltar |last=Chaves |first=Fabio |date=27 May 2019 |website=Vista-Se |access-date=25 July 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612175723/https://www.vista-se.com.br/anitta-revela-que-deixou-de-ser-vegana-mas-diz-que-ja-esta-fazendo-adaptacoes-para-voltar/ |archive-date=12 June 2019}}</ref> [[People for the Ethical Treatment of Animals|PETA]] named her one of the Most Beautiful Vegan Celebrities of 2022, along with singer/songwriter [[Lenny Kravitz]].<ref>{{Cite magazine |first1=Hannah |last1=Dailey |title=Lenny Kravitz & Anitta Named PETA's Most Beautiful Vegan Celebrities of 2022: Exclusive |url=https://www.billboard.com/music/music-news/lenny-kravitz-anitta-peta-most-beautiful-vegan-celebrities-2022-1235114165/ |magazine=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |date= 14 July 2022}}</ref>

Anitta follows [[Candomblé]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=Pinotti |first=Fernanda |title=Anitta compartilha fotos no candomblé e anuncia clipe novo |url=https://www.cnnbrasil.com.br/entretenimento/anitta-compartilha-fotos-no-candomble-e-anuncia-clipe-novo/#:~:text=No%20in%C3%ADcio%20de%202023,%20a,no%20dia%20da%20Consci%C3%AAncia%20Negra. |access-date=2024-12-15 |website=CNN Brasil |date=13 May 2024 |language=pt-BR}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-05-14 |title=Candomblé: qual a origem da religião que fez Anitta perder seguidores? |url=https://educacao.uol.com.br/noticias/2024/05/14/candomble-qual-a-origem-da-religiao-que-fez-anitta-perder-seguidores.htm |access-date=2024-12-15 |website=UOL |language=pt-br}}</ref>

=== Philanthropy and advocacy ===
Anitta is an environmental activist, vocally advocating against the crimes committed in the [[Amazon rainforest]] and supporting the rights of its [[Indigenous peoples|indigenous population]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=Hypeness |first=Redação |date=23 August 2019 |title=Anitta se posiciona em defesa da Amazônia: 'Pode mandar ameaça e xingar, não me preocupo' |url=https://www.hypeness.com.br/2019/08/anitta-se-posiciona-em-defesa-da-amazonia-pode-mandar-ameaca-e-xingar-nao-me-preocupo/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220327101155/https://www.hypeness.com.br/2019/08/anitta-se-posiciona-em-defesa-da-amazonia-pode-mandar-ameaca-e-xingar-nao-me-preocupo/ |archive-date=27 March 2022 |access-date=27 March 2022 |website=Hypeness |language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta posta desabafo sobre queimadas na Amazônia e questão indígena - Emais |url=https://emais.estadao.com.br/noticias/gente,anitta-posta-desabafo-sobre-queimadas-na-amazonia-e-questao-indigena,70002976904 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211201124944/https://emais.estadao.com.br/noticias/gente,anitta-posta-desabafo-sobre-queimadas-na-amazonia-e-questao-indigena,70002976904 |archive-date=1 December 2021 |access-date=27 March 2022 |website=Estadão |language=pt-BR}}</ref> During the 2018 [[Elections in Brazil|Brazilian elections]], she publicly joined the #EleNão (#NotHim) campaign, opposing presidential candidate [[Jair Bolsonaro]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=Hypeness |first=Redação |date=24 September 2018 |title=Anitta adere ao movimento #EleNão e desafia Ivete Sangalo e Claudia Leitte |url=https://www.hypeness.com.br/2018/09/anitta-adere-ao-movimento-elenao-e-desafia-ivete-sangalo-e-clauda-leitte/ |access-date=27 March 2022 |website=Hypeness |language=en-US |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925165752/https://www.hypeness.com.br/2018/09/anitta-adere-ao-movimento-elenao-e-desafia-ivete-sangalo-e-clauda-leitte/ |archive-date=September 25, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.opovo.com.br/noticias/brasil/2021/11/23/anitta-rebate-critica-de-bolsonaro-tambem-faria-isso-se-eu-fosse-ruim.html |date=23 November 2021 |title=Anitta rebate crítica de Bolsonaro: "Também faria isso se eu fosse ruim!" |access-date=27 March 2022 |website=O POVO |language=pt-br}}</ref> She also advocates for [[climate change]], conservation, the environment, the [[right to food]] and [[Right to health|health]]. She has already made several donations to [[Non-governmental organization|NGOs]], [[Charitable organization|charities]] and needy communities, including donations to combat [[poverty]] in favelas,<ref>{{Cite web |last= |first= |date=2022-10-03 |title=Anitta doa R$ 500 mil a ONG que combate a pobreza nas favelas |url=https://www.correiobraziliense.com.br/diversao-e-arte/2022/10/5041605-anitta-doa-rs-500-mil-a-ong-que-combate-a-pobreza-nas-favelas.html |access-date=2024-11-11 |website=[[Correio Braziliense]] |language=pt-BR}}</ref> [[2024 Brazil wildfires|fires in the Amazon]]<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-08-30 |title=Brigada de Alter recebe doação de Anitta para combate a incêndios na Amazônia |url=https://g1.globo.com/pa/santarem-regiao/noticia/2024/08/30/brigada-de-alter-recebe-doacao-de-anitta-para-combate-a-incendios-na-amazonia.ghtml |access-date=2024-11-11 |website=G1 |language=pt-br}}</ref> and to the non-governmental organization "Zuzu for Africa", which takes care of African children; the money was used to purchase a property and transform it into a dental and [[Hospital|medical center]] for needy families and children in [[Africa]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=Valbão |first=Mariana |title=Crianças de ONG da África agradecem Anitta por doação para novo hospital |url=https://www.cnnbrasil.com.br/entretenimento/criancas-de-ong-da-africa-agradecem-anitta-por-doacao-para-novo-hospital/ |access-date=2024-11-11 |website=CNN Brasil |date=30 October 2023 |language=pt-BR}}</ref>

As part of the [[LGBTQ community]], Anitta defends the [[LGBTQ rights in Brazil|rights of people in the community]], including the non-interference of religion in [[Civil and political rights|civil rights]], such as [[domestic partnership]] and [[Same-sex marriage|marriage]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2017-06-18 |title=Anitta diz na Parada Gay que orientação sexual 'não tem a ver' com religião |url=https://g1.globo.com/sao-paulo/noticia/anitta-diz-na-parada-gay-que-orientacao-sexual-nao-tem-a-ver-com-religiao.ghtml |access-date=2024-11-11 |website=G1 |language=pt-br}}</ref> To the magazine ''[[Gay Times]]'', she, who is bisexual, stated that part of the media [[Bisexual erasure|pretends not to know or ignores]] her sexual orientation out of prejudice.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Corner |first=Lewis |date=2021-05-28 |title=Anitta talks LGBTQ+ visibility and bi-erasure as she covers GAY TIMES Magazine |url=https://www.gaytimes.com/culture/anitta-talks-lgbtq-visibility-and-bi-erasure-as-she-covers-gay-times-magazine/ |access-date=2024-11-11 |website=GAY TIMES |language=en-GB}}</ref>

In 2025 Trans Visibility Day, Anitta expressed she admires [[transgender people]], saying 'One day in the life of a free person, who loves themselves, respects themselves, accepts themselves as they are, is worth more than 100 years in the life of a person who points the finger at others.', citing [[The Buddha]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-01-31 |title=Anitta defende liberdade e respeito no Dia da Visibilidade Trans |url=https://www.itatiaia.com.br/entretenimento/2025/01/30/anitta-defende-liberdade-e-respeito-no-dia-da-visibilidade-trans |access-date=2025-03-25 |website=Rádio Itatiaia |language=pt-BR}}</ref>

Anitta has taken a stand in defense of [[Women's rights in Brazil|women's rights]] on several occasions, such as in demonstrations against bills that [[History of abortion#Criminalization|criminalize abortion]] and in encouraging [[Women's suffrage|women to vote]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta protesta contra projeto de lei que equipara aborto a homicídio |url=https://www.cfemea.org.br/index.php/pt/radar-feminista-lista/direito-ao-aborto/9472-anitta-protesta-contra-projeto-de-lei-que-equipara-aborto-a-homicidio#:~:text=Anitta%20protesta%20contra%20projeto%20de%20lei%20que%20equipara%20aborto%20a%20homic%C3%ADdio,-A%20cantora%20se&text=Anitta%20compartilhou%20um%20texto%20nas,Anitta%20e%20outras%20personalidades%20p%C3%BAblicas.&text=Nos%20stories%20do%20Instagram,%20Anitta,estupradores%20por%20seis%20at%C3%A9%20dez. |access-date=2024-11-11 |website=Cfemea.org}}</ref>

2017 [[Multishow Brazilian Music Awards]] presented her shows featuring [[people with disabilities]] and [[Plus-size model|plus size]] models as her dancers.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta agora tem bailarinos com Síndrome de Down e deficiência física |url=https://www.uol.com.br/universa/noticias/redacao/2017/10/18/anitta-agora-tem-bailarinos-com-sindrome-de-down-e-deficiencia-fisica.htm |access-date=2025-03-25 |website=www.uol.com.br |language=pt-br}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2017-11-12 |title=Cadeirante que dançou com Anitta é casada com deficiente acrobata e planeja filhos |url=https://extra.globo.com/famosos/cadeirante-que-dancou-com-anitta-casada-com-deficiente-acrobata-planeja-filhos-22059452.html |access-date=2025-03-25 |website=Extra Online |language=pt-BR}}</ref> A dancer with [[Down syndrome]] said 'I loved it'.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Anitta apresenta novo bailarino com síndrome de Down: 'Eu amei' |url=https://www.estadao.com.br/emais/comportamento/anitta-apresenta-novo-bailarino-com-sindrome-de-down-eu-amei/ |access-date=2025-03-25 |website=Estadão |language=pt-br}}</ref> In 2019, she also announced Makayla Sabino, a trans [[Ballarina dancer|ballarina]], for [[Rock In Rio]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-10-04 |title=Anitta terá bailarina trans em show no Rock in Rio: 'É uma mulher e ponto' |url=https://oglobo.globo.com/cultura/anitta-tera-bailarina-trans-em-show-no-rock-in-rio-uma-mulher-ponto-23997198 |access-date=2025-03-25 |website=O Globo |language=pt-BR}}</ref> Sabino eventually starred in a [[docuseries]] transmitted by [[Globoplay]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-07-02 |title=Ex-bailarina trans de Anitta é estrela de doc do Globoplay e há três anos tenta vaquinha para cirurgia |url=https://extra.globo.com/famosos/noticia/2024/07/ex-bailarina-trans-de-anitta-e-estrela-de-doc-do-globoplay-e-ha-tres-anos-tenta-vaquinha-para-cirurgia.ghtml |access-date=2025-03-25 |website=extra |language=pt-br}}</ref>

