* [[David Burke (British actor)|David Burke]] as Camillo
* [[Robert Stephens]] as Polixenes
* [[Jeremy Kemp]] as [[Leontes]]
* [[Anna Calder-Marshall]] as Hermione
* Jeremy Dimmick as Mamillius
* [[Merelina Kendall]] as Emilia
* [[Susan Brodrick]] as Lady to Hermione
* [[Leonard Kavanagh]] as Lord to Leontes
* [[John Bailey (British actor)|John Bailey]] as Lord to Leontes
* [[Cyril Luckham]] as Antigonus
* [[William Relton]] as Lord to Leontes
* [[Margaret Tyzack]] as Paulina
