* First transmitted in the US: 17 May 1982
* Running time (PAL DVD): 190 minutes
'''Cast'''
{{Castlist|
* [[Charles Gray (actor)|Charles Gray]] as [[Pandarus]]
* [[Anton Lesser]] as [[Troilus]]
* [[Tony Steedman]] as [[Aeneas]]
