'''Cast'''
{{Castlist|
* [[Jonathan Kent (director)|Jonathan Kent]] as The King of Navarre
* [[Christopher Blake]] as Longaville
* [[Geoffrey Burridge]] as Dumain
* [[Mike Gwilym]] as Berowne
* [[David Warner (actor)|David Warner]] as Don Armado
* [[John Kane (writer)|John Kane]] as Moth
* [[Paul Jesson]] as [[Costard]]
* [[Frank Williams (actor)|Frank Williams]] as Dull
* [[Paddy Navin]] as Jaquenetta
